273
00:16:30,160 --> 00:16:31,957
Pardon.

274
00:16:33,039 --> 00:16:35,792
Je m‘appelle Amy Farrah Fowler.
On s‘est vus, l‘autre soir.

275
00:16:36,079 --> 00:16:38,354
